{"tid":59912,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人咳左半年都仲咳緊?","createTime":"2016-12-30T05:02:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-11T09:44:19.000Z","uid":37652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7b0b35cabb5c8af7c3391768ab7845395c96e951","tid":59912,"uid":37652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T05:02:15.000Z","msg":"本身哮喘底，我咳左成半年，中西醫都睇哂都無用，但係又唔係哮喘發，肺照埋都係好清，有無人知可以點算?"},{"pid":"033ba5ca3813a2eb5516ea8de24eb30f622d2d59","tid":59912,"uid":2894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T05:03:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>本身哮喘底，我咳左成半年，中西醫都睇哂都無用，但係又唔係哮喘發，肺照埋都係好清，有無人知可以點算?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n試下洗鼻，鼻水唔倒流會減少咳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4054fb92643f17197fbcdf18dc44513a2afdb87b","tid":59912,"uid":24536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T05:05:03.000Z","msg":"唉我氣管敏感都咳到仆街"},{"pid":"d293da723e6d33789adfcb6c7190fc215734be55","tid":59912,"uid":19657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T05:05:09.000Z","msg":"照咩先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> X光定CT"},{"pid":"6e648739d2c050bafc1886d793f7ef92012bf16c","tid":59912,"uid":37652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T05:05:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>照咩先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> X光定CT</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nX光"},{"pid":"5cd9b4b8debe40be9826475e8b820742f45b2137","tid":59912,"uid":37652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T05:06:57.000Z","msg":"前日入左急症睇話我咩上呼吸道感染，食左抗生素都好似無咩好轉，之前就係無啖咳，依幾日嚴重左加埋有啖"},{"pid":"189600740ddb8a90a2fd061541c480a7b881ff8c","tid":59912,"uid":37652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T05:08:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唉我氣管敏感都咳到仆街</blockquote><br />\n有d醫生都係話氣管敏感，但係應該會有方法減緩架"},{"pid":"1a228ceeaa41b0057c6bba885d664a49c56b1449","tid":59912,"uid":22132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit